data.description: Come see this luxurious custom-built Hurst home that will take your breath away. With such precise attention to detail, this home looks modern in every aspect, with every upgrade, but without having to pay any city tax. The stained wood accents matched with the light and dark complected granite throughout pairs perfectly with the dark wooden flooring. The open concept kitchen and dining area is a hosts dream for friends and family members to entertain and enjoy. Tray ceiling master, with walk-in shower and seperate garden tub, and custom barn doors shows all attention to detail was accomplished. Stop by and take a look yourself, this home is ready and waiting for you.
